title: PNotes.NET 3.3.0.3 Portable Sticky Notes And Reminders
description:
Portable Sticky Notes And Reminders


Download, unzip and use.  It is portable and free.



Publisher	Andrey Gruber 
Price	Free
Version	3.3.0.3	
Last updated	Sep 15, 2016
File Size	3.70 Mb	
Requirements	.NET Framework 4.5


PNotes.NET is a portable sticky notes application that offers a highly customizable set of features that include reminder notes with alarm, font formatting, smileys, note sharing via email, color customization, password protection, linking between notes, encryption, FTP synchronization, and much more.
You can also keep daily notes as part of a personal diary and optionally hide notes from view, schedule them to appear at specific times and manage all your notes from the Control Panel.
Other features include integrated web search, integrated backup, support for skins, and more.
PNotes.NET offers several additional features over the older PNotes program (from the same author), including tables, free drawing, encryption, cloud synchronization and additional export options.


Reality Ascent by Dragan Glavasic
